gw.plugin.rateflow

Interface IImpactTestingPlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin, java.rmi.Remote

    public interface IImpactTestingPlugin
extends com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin
    Implementations of this plugin manage the creation and quoting of baseline periods and test periods as well as constraining the available rate books when quoting the test periods.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      PolicyPeriod createBaselinePeriod(PolicyPeriod original)
      Create the baseline period based on the original bound period for purposes of observing the impact a rating change has on premiums.

      • setAlternateRatebooks

        void setAlternateRatebooks(java.util.List<ImpactTestingRateBook> ratebooks)
        Set the alternate ratebooks to be used for rating test periods. These will override date-based restrictions when querying for ratebooks. Pass null for no override.
        Parameters:
        ratebooks - desired RateBooks, or null.
